<p>Amazon’s cloud division, Amazon Web Services (AWS), experienced a widespread outage on Monday, acknowledging an “operational issue” that affected multiple services and led to increased error rates and latency in its US-EAST-1 region [ft.com#1][scmp.com#1][dawn.com#1]. The disruption made it difficult for users around the world to access numerous apps and sites, including Snapchat, Roblox, Signal and Duolingo, while several Amazon-owned services—such as its main retail site, Prime Video and Alexa—also faced problems [theguardian.com#1][nytimes.com#1][aljazeera.com#1]. AWS said it is working on multiple parallel paths to accelerate recovery, and news outlets reported users in Asia, including Singapore, were also affected [theglobeandmail.com#1][straitstimes.com#1][bbc.co.uk#1].</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/pZyJxAMbZbGoSJrAK8VgWQnw0_3N1NvZnPjTTWaMzSsrArWpub7TPJYOYpia4oD-N-wsdYjVzZT0RVn40psvrcGqKwkXcCbklYwl0p3tVl1JAY1rWjYLB_z9n8XgPcWwD4qsiv0vub6NDj5OZeW55JPM_VPKWsJFjxLb7SC2eOXKpgG4fcZ8oUk9_rAk4Z77OLY6KzcIB0aQemhB_bcrjG0tVpiAmKFSXPHFFRRBw7Yfgq-yL_OfJ9jnvjHXKHDooLbCT-yeCtF0KjLTHQ' alt='Amazon Web Services branding on display at a technology conference in Paris.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Finance platforms: Coinbase and Robinhood reported service issues and attributed them to AWS, highlighting exposure of trading and crypto services to cloud incidents [scmp.com#1][aljazeera.com#1].</li><li>Gaming disruptions: Fortnite and Supercell titles like Clash Royale and Clash of Clans experienced downtime linked to the AWS outage, according to media reports [michaelwest.com.au#1][dawn.com#1].</li><li>Payments affected: Payments apps Venmo and neobank Chime encountered problems during the incident, according to outage tracking and media coverage [michaelwest.com.au#1][dawn.com#1].</li><li>Mobility apps: Ride‑hailing service Lyft’s app was down for thousands of users in the United States during the outage window [michaelwest.com.au#1][dawn.com#1].</li><li>Post‑CrowdStrike context: This is the first major global internet disruption widely noted since last year’s CrowdStrike malfunction that hobbled systems in hospitals, banks and airports [theglobeandmail.com#1].</li></ul><blockquote>We are working on multiple parallel paths to accelerate recovery - Amazon Web Services</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Perplexity (AI startup): CEO Aravind Srinivas said the service was down due to an AWS issue and that the team was working on a fix. (<a href='https://michaelwest.com.au/websites-apps-down-in-amazon-cloud-unit-outage/'>Michael West Media</a>)</li><li>Downdetector: The crowdsourced outage tracker showed problems reported for Amazon’s shopping site, Prime Video and Alexa during the incident. (<a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1950151/amazons-cloud-unit-reports-outage-several-websites-down'>Dawn</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.dw.com/en/outage-at-amazon-cloud-service-unit-causes-major-disruption/a-74421381'>Outage at Amazon cloud service unit causes major disruption</a> - dw.com</li><li><a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/10/20/amazon-cloud-problems-spur-outage-of-global-websites-and-apps'>Amazon cloud problems spur outage of global websites and apps</a> - aljazeera.com</li><li><a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/world/united-states-canada/article/3329687/amazons-aws-outage-disrupts-fortnite-snapchat-and-major-apps-worldwide'>From Fortnite to Alexa, Amazon’s AWS outage causes global outage</a> - scmp.com</li><li><a href='https://www.ft.com/content/f9d13a0e-9378-429c-9be0-5f15f649cc3f'>Amazon’s cloud business hit by outage</a> - ft.com</li><li><a href='https://www.theglobeandmail.com/business/international-business/article-amazons-cloud-unit-aws-reports-outage-several-websites-down/'>Amazon’s cloud unit AWS reports outage; several websites down</a> - theglobeandmail.com</li><li><a href='https://michaelwest.com.au/websites-apps-down-in-amazon-cloud-unit-outage/'>Websites, apps down in Am